ūjāyidaṃ phalaṃ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap558:26.1":{"pli":"Imaṃ khāda imaṃ bhuñja, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap558:26.2":{"pli":"imamhi sayane saya; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap558:26.3":{"pli":"Labhāmi sabbamevetaṃ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap558:26.4":{"pli":"buddhapūjāyidaṃ phalaṃ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap558:27.1":{"pli":"Sabbattha pūjito homi, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap558:27.2":{"pli":"yaso accuggato mama; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap558:27.3":{"pli":"Mahāpakkho sadā homi, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap558:27.4":{"pli":"abhejjapariso sadā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap558:27.5":{"pli":"Ñātīnaṃ uttamo homi, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap558:27.6":{"pli":"buddhapūjāyidaṃ phalaṃ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap558:28.1":{"pli":"Sītaṃ uṇhaṃ na jānāmi, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap558:28.2":{"pli":"pariḷāho na vijjati; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap558:28.3":{"pli":"Atho cetasikaṃ dukkhaṃ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap558:28.4":{"pli":"hadaye me na vijjati. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap558:29.1":{"pli":"Suvaṇṇavaṇṇo hutvāna, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap558:29.2":{"pli":"saṃsarāmi bhavābhave; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap558:29.3":{"pli":"Vevaṇṇiyaṃ na jānāmi, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap558:29.4":{"pli":"buddhapūjāyidaṃ phalaṃ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap558:30.1":{"pli":"Devalokā cavitvāna, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap558:30.2":{"pli":"sukkamūlena codito; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap558:30.3":{"p